lgp.core.evolution.fitness

Class FitnessEvaluator<TData>

  • lgp.core.evolution.fitness.FitnessEvaluator<TData>
  • Type Parameters:
    TData - The type of the program being evaluated.

    public class FitnessEvaluator<TData>

    Provides a way to evaluate the fitness of a program.

    This is done by using the class FitnessContext that is register with the class Environment.

    See Also:
    class FitnessContext, class Environment
